I'm Peter Buchard, and I worked at Playdead in Copenhagen.

12
00:00:29,698 --> 00:00:30,818
I worked on Limbo and Inside.

13
00:00:31,518 --> 00:00:33,959
And I'm currently at Studio Gobo in Brighton, England,

14
00:00:34,059 --> 00:00:35,560
where we worked on Disney Infinity,

15
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:37,621
and we're currently working on a big co-op devs

16
